                  <interp inst="t18220220-40-crimeloc217" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-40-off213 t18220220-40-crimeloc217"></join>. On the 7th of February, about four o'clock, I was called from the bar into the tap-room, and was told a man had stolen a pot. The prisoner was brought in, and I saw it found in his breeches; it had my name and sign on it; the name is now erased. I understand his wife has gone to live with another man, which has affected his mind.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220220-40-person476">
                  JAMES 
                  STONE
               <interp inst="t18220220-40-person476" type="surname" value="STONE"></interp>
